  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAs far as I can tell, the REVERT reason encoding is not canonically defined in any documentation, and is best pieced together from the [solidity PR that introduced it](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/pull/3364) and [this comment on EIP 838](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/838#issuecomment-458919375). Since it is now an important part of the Ethereum Contract ABI, I think it should be specified on the \"Contract ABI Specification\" page.",
